
set oven to 170
cook
 - 300 g buckwheat pasta
rinse

meanwhile
combine
 - 1/2 cup vegetable broth
 - 3 tbsp soy sauce
 - 1 tbsp mirin
 - 1 tbsp hoisin sauce
 - 1 tbsp fresh grated ginger
 - 1 grated garlic clove
set aside

prepare
 - 1 cup grated carrots
 - 1/2 cup grated radished
 - 2 minced green onions split between green and white parts
 - 1 cup minced boston lettuce
 - 1/2 cup cilantro
 - 1/3 cup chopped peanuts

combine
 - 1 lbs diced tofu
 - 1/4 cup corn startch
 - 1/2 tsp chinese 5 spice
cook tofu in a large pan
set in a plate
keep warm in oven

add sauce to pan
add white part of green onions
simmer covered 2 minutes

meanwhile
place noodles in 3-4 bowls
top with vegetables

combine in a small bowl
 - 1 tsp corn startch
 - 1 tbsp water
add to sauce
cook until thickened

add tofu to bowl
top with sauce
top with peanuts
top with cilantro

serves 3-4

#quick #asian
